{{Quote|Gee.|[[Anakin Solo]] witnessing the aftermath of the destruction of the Great Temple near the Unnh River|<ref name="EoVI">''[[The New Jedi Order: Edge of Victory I: Conquest]]''</ref>}}
The '''Unnh River''' was located on [[Yavin 4/Legends|Yavin 4]] and was likely named for the [[Sullustan/Legends|Sullustan]] [[Scout/Legends|explorer]] [[Dr'uun Unnh/Legends|Dr'uun Unnh]].<ref name="SoR" /> The river wound its way through the [[Wayward Jungle]], the [[Isle of Kun]], the [[Val'Arnos Jungle]] and the [[Ersham Ridge]], passing close to the [[Palace of the Woolamander]] and the [[Great Temple/Legends|Great Temple]]. The stream formed a river delta, known as the [[Taurin Delta]], as it entered an ocean. The [[Temple of the Blueleaf Cluster/Legends|Temple of the Blueleaf Cluster]] was located atop the Taurin Delta.<ref name="SWG" />

During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], the [[Mining Outpost (Yavin 4)|Mining Outpost]] and the [[Imperial Fortress (Yavin 4)|Imperial Fortress]] were built near the river banks.<ref name="SWG" /> The [[Yuuzhan Vong]] built their base along the Unnh River in [[26 ABY/Legends|26 ABY]], during the [[Invasion of Yavin 4]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]].<ref name="EoVI" />

